bluemoose.mediator

Interface MediatorInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MediatorImpl

    public interface MediatorInterface
    A mediator is responsible for handling requests made from a translator, in a manner independently of the translator, and routing requests to the correct data access component. It deals entirely with java objects.
